                ReqIFName="High Throughput Data Capacity" ReqIFText="The communication system shall support high-throughput data transfer. Rationale:Enables detailed image and video sharing.">
              <ownedRelations xsi:type="CapellaRequirements:CapellaIncomingRelation"
